<h1>Instructions</h1>
<ul class="instructions-text">
	<li>Please read the instructions carefully.</li>
	<li>This task is for non-profit research purposes. The objective is to <b> measure the attractiveness of a place </b> as illustrated through Google Street View images.</li>
	<li>You will be shown 11 image sets of different places in Amsterdam.</li>
	<li>Each place is represented by 4 images taken from 4 different directions in clockwise direction.
    <li>For each place, please answer the questions by selecting the appropriate options.</li>
    <li>Please note that you are <b> evaluating the place </b> as illustrated in the images.</li>
    <li>After answering all the questions in a page, click 'Next' to continue with the next image.</li>
    <li>After finishing the task, you will receive a survey code</li>
</ul>

<p><em>Please note that <b>there is no right or wrong answer</b>.</em></p>


